casebody.data:
No. 635. Southern Railway Company, Petitioner, v. Hubbard Brothers & Co. March 25, 1907. Mr. W. A. Henderson, Mr. Caruthers Ewing and Mr. Alfred P. Thom for petitioner. No appearance for respondent.

Petition for a

writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
